div.div: Change self bot's nickname in discord.js
Get the guild via id. ie .guilds.cache.get("guild id") Updating the nickname is simply, just call .me.setNickname("new nickname") - it'll error if it doesn't have enough permissions.
VS Code how to open a window does not install any extension?

to remove all extensions for that one window, type code --disable-extensions. If you want to remove a specific one, code --disable-extension id.extension-name. For example, code --disable-extension belfz.search-crates-io to disable the search crates.io extension for that window.
Reset visual studio to the default setting
Do a clean install of it. Uninstall and re-run the installer.
Property 'style' does not exist on type but still work
Restart the TS language server, or, restart VSCode.
Toggle/Disable real-time Markdown preview update in VSCode?
I suggest shutting the webview / panel and then only opening when you need to. I'm pretty sure you can find extensions that only update on save, but I'm not sure.
VSCode Settings Sync: how to see previous versions of my settings.json?
If you click the ones below it with something like 8 minutes ago it'll open a diff.
